Central module PG6UV
With the patented technology of double pass through the reverse osmosis membrane.
Key Features:
Rated capacity: 1.6 GPH ( 6 LPH )
Maximum capacity: 2.4 GPH ( 9 LPH )
Number of separately controlled humidification zones: 2
Voltage: 24 VDC + 48 VDC
Output pressure: 1000 psi ( 70 bar )
Power consumption: 200 W
Housing and inner mechanical parts material: high quality aluminum
Dimensions WxDxH, in (mm): 24 x 16 x 13 ( 600 x 400 x 330 )
  • Very low power consumption
  • Silent operation, the device is suitable for mounting near living areas
  • Internal hydraulic valves - no source of noise in the room
  • Completely automatic operation
  • High degree of demineralization - 97...99%
  • Microbiological safety - eliminates viruses, bacteria, fungi
  • Leakage control inside the case and on high pressure line
  • Automatic antiscale function
Advantages:
  • Continuous UV water sterilization
The equipment is produced in branded aluminum cases with an original design. All rights reserved.
